thereesys-escript Credits
====================

Escript is the product of years of work by many people.


Current Research and Development Team
--------------------------------------

The active researchers and developers for the current release series are listed
here in alphabetical order. While development is collaborative, each person is
listed with some of their major contributions - this list is not exhaustive.

Andrea Codd
  Documentation, Python code

Adam Ellery
  Maintenance of escript module, release wrangler

Ander Garro
  Development and testing

Lutz Gross
  Patriarch, technical lead, solvers, large chunks of the original code

Qi Shao
  Trilinos testing


Previous Contributors by Release
---------------------------------

The following individuals contributed to previous releases of esys-escript:

Current Contributors (Releases 5.5 and later):
  Andrea Codd (since 5.5)
  Cihan Altinay (since 2.0) - Weipa visualisation package, SCons build
    system rework, Ripley and CUDA solvers, Trilinos integration
  Joel Fenwick (since 2.0) - Lazy evaluation, maintenance of escript module,
    release wrangler
  Lutz Gross (since 1.0)
  Qi Shao (since 5.1)
  Adam Ellery
  Ander Garro

